find serial number by typing 
>udevadm info -a -n /dev/ttyUSB5 | grep serial

get: 
 ATTRS{serial}=="A1032GHY"
 ATTRS{serial}=="tegra-xhci"


for pxhawk 

    ATTRS{serial}=="A6023M03"
    ATTRS{serial}=="tegra-ehci.0"


for leddarone 
 ATTRS{serial}=="A1032GHY"
 ATTRS{serial}=="tegra-xhci"

write rules here 
/etc/udev/rules.d/99-usbserial.rules

